trans-unit.source: Identifies the operating system, or platform, supported by an assembly.
trans-unit.target: Identifiserer operativsystemet eller plattformen som støttes av en samling.

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Environment.OSVersion%2A?displayProperty=fullName> and <xref:System.OperatingSystem.Platform%2A?displayProperty=fullName> properties to obtain the PlatformID enumeration for the currently executing operating system or development platform.
trans-unit.target: Bruk av <xref:System.Environment.OSVersion%2A?displayProperty=fullName>og <xref:System.OperatingSystem.Platform%2A?displayProperty=fullName>Egenskaper for å hente PlatformID-nummerering for øyeblikket kjøres operative system eller utvikling plattformen.</xref:System.OperatingSystem.Platform%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Environment.OSVersion%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Use the PlatformID enumeration to help determine whether the current operating system or development platform supports your application.
trans-unit.target: Bruk PlatformID opplistingen til å avgjøre om det gjeldende operativsystemet eller utviklingsplattform støtter programmet.

trans-unit.source: You can use the underlying integer value of each PlatformID enumeration member, as shown in the table, as the `PlatformId` argument for the [SignTool.exe (Sign Tool)](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) utility.
trans-unit.target: Du kan bruke den underliggende heltallsverdien til medlemmene PlatformID opplisting som vises i tabellen, som den `PlatformId` argumentet for den [SignTool.exe (logg verktøyet)](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) verktøyet.
| Medlemmet | Underliggende verdien | |------------|----------------------| | Win32S |&0; | | Win32Windows |&1; | | Win32NT |&2; | | WinCE |&3; | | UNIX |&4; | | Xbox |&5; | | MacOSX |&6; |

trans-unit.source: The operating system is Windows NT or later.
trans-unit.target: Operativsystemet er Windows NT eller senere.

trans-unit.source: Win32s is a layer that runs on 16-bit versions of Windows to provide access to 32-bit applications.
trans-unit.target: Win32s er et lag som kjører på 16-biters versjoner av Windows for å gi tilgang til 32-biters applikasjoner.

trans-unit.source: The operating system is Windows 95 or Windows 98.
The operating system is Windows CE.
